---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact" description="Book a free 20-minute automation consultation. Tell me what you're doing manually.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">
            Let's talk
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-8">
            Tell me what's eating up your time. I'll tell you what we can automate first.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-4">What to include</h2>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-stone-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>What manual tasks are taking up time?</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>What tools/apps are involved?</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-copper shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Rough timeline and budget (if you have one)</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Prefer to schedule directly?</h3>
              <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">
                Book a free 20-minute call to discuss your automation needs.
              </p>
              <a href="https://calendly.com/mnehmos" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-stone-900 text-stone-50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
                Open Calendly
              </a>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mt-2">

              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-3">Or email directly</h3>
              <a href="mailto:Mnehmos@gmail.com" class="text-copper hover:underline">
                Mnehmos@gmail.com
              </a>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mt-1">

              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 p-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-6">Send a message</h2>
          
          <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjarbvq" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Honeypot for spam -->
            <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none" />
            
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Name</label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="name" 
                name="name" 
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-copper focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all"
                placeholder="Your name"
              />
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Email</label>
              <input 
                type="email" 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-copper focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all"
                placeholder="you@company.com"
              />
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Company <span class="text-stone-400">(optional)</span></label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="company" 
                name="company"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-copper focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all"
                placeholder="Your company"
              />
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="project-type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">What are you looking for?</label>
              <select 
                id="project-type" 
                name="project-type"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-copper focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all bg-white"
              >
                <option value="">Select an option...</option>
                <option value="workflow-automation">Workflow Automation</option>
                <option value="ai-agent">Custom AI Agent</option>
                <option value="integration">Tool Integration</option>
                <option value="internal-tool">Internal Tool / Dashboard</option>
                <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-2">Tell me about the problem</label>
              <textarea 
                id="message" 
                name="message" 
                rows="5" 
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-stone-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-copper focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all resize-none"
                placeholder="What manual tasks are eating up your time? What tools are involved? What would success look like?"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <button 
              type="submit"
              class="w-full bg-stone-900 text-stone-50 px-6 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
            >
              Send message
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
            
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs text-center">
              I'll get back to you within 24 hours.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Local info -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">
        Serving Safford + remote teams
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Based in Safford, Arizona (Graham County). I work with local businesses in Eastern Arizona and remote teams across the country. All consultations are available via video call.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
